At PCHC, we make having x-rays taken easy for people with busy lives. As a PCHC patient, you don't need to go anywhere else - PCHC operates two full service x-ray departments for your convenience.

X-rays ordered by your PCHC provider can be taken at Helen Hunt Health Center in Old Town or Brewer Medical Center in Brewer. Our on-site x-ray machines allows us to obtain immediate information about an acute injury.

